sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as User
    participant LS as Live Service
    participant V as Viewer Count Service
    participant R as Redis
    participant K as Kafka

    Note over U,K: 2. Join Stream
    U->>V: POST /streams/{streamId}/join
    V->>R: EXISTS active_stream:{streamId}
    R-->>V: 1 (active) or 0 (not found)
    alt stream active
        V->>K: publish ViewerJoined {streamId, userId}
        V-->>U: 200 OK
        K->>V: consume ViewerJoined
        V->>R: SADD stream:{streamId}:viewers {userId}
        R-->>V: 1 (new) or 0 (duplicate)
        alt new viewer
            V->>R: INCR viewer_count
            V->>R: SETEX viewer:{userId} 60
        else duplicate
            V->>R: SETEX viewer:{userId} 60
        end
    else stream not active
        V-->>U: 400 Bad Request
    end

    Note over U,K: 3. Leave Stream
    U->>V: POST /streams/{streamId}/leave
    V->>K: publish ViewerLeft {streamId, userId}
    V-->>U: 200 OK
    K->>V: consume ViewerLeft
    V->>R: SREM stream:{streamId}:viewers {userId}
    R-->>V: 1 (removed) or 0 (not found)
    alt removed
        V->>R: DECR viewer_count
        V->>R: DEL viewer:{userId}
    else not found
        Note over V: Ignore
    end

    Note over LS,K: 4. Stream Ended
    LS->>K: publish StreamEnded {streamId}
    K->>V: consume StreamEnded
    V->>R: DEL active_stream:{streamId}
    V->>R: DEL stream:{streamId}:viewer_count
    V->>R: DEL stream:{streamId}:viewers
    R-->>V: OK

    Note over U,R: 5. Get Viewer Count
    U->>V: GET /streams/{streamId}/viewers
    V->>R: GET viewer_count
    R-->>V: N
    V-->>U: 200 OK {viewerCount: N}